---
title: Breakfast Champion's Chilaquiles with Black Beans, Eggs, and Poblano Chili
description: Chee-lah-kee-lays! Even just saying that name out loud is enough to put you in a brighter mood. And if you haven’t yet discovered the wonder that is chilaquiles, think of it as what happens when nachos go to brunch. Based around shreds of tortilla smothered in a feisty mix of black bean, tomato, chile, and cheese and finished with egg perched on top, it fills you up and gives you the energy to power through the day like the true champ you are.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/breakfast-champions-chilaquiles-dbfe6dab.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/breakfast-champions-chilaquiles-9de9f577.pdf
